{
  "texts": [
    "Wearable IoT devices can be used to detect falls in elderly patients and individuals with balance problems.",
    "DL models can analyze the data from these devices to detect falls and alert healthcare providers or family members.",
    "Wearable IoT devices can be used to monitor medication adherence in patients with chronic diseases.",
    "DL models can analyze the data from these devices to provide feedback on medication adherence and improve patient outcomes.",
    "DL models can be used to develop early warning systems for critical health events such as heart attacks and strokes."
  ]
}